{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.240", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.160", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was ist uns unsere Sicherheit wert? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Frage m\u00fcssen wir uns als gew\u00e4hlte deutsche Volksvertreter stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.920", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke hat diese Frage f\u00fcr sich heute eindeutig beantwortet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.640", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht viel bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.120", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gar nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.720", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anders kann man den Antrag der Linken nicht verstehen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anders kann man es nicht verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn in Zeiten sich ver\u00e4ndernder globaler Sicherheitslagen solche verantwortungslosen Forderungen gestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.080", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und es w\u00e4re verantwortungslos, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.720", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir auf diese ver\u00e4nderten Gegebenheiten nicht reagieren w\u00fcrden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherheit m\u00fcssen wir zunehmend global denken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bedrohungslage hat sich in den vergangenen Jahren ver\u00e4ndert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Krisen im Osten oder in Afrika haben direkte Auswirkungen auf unser Leben in Europa."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Fl\u00fcchtlingskrise hat uns das eindr\u00fccklich vor Augen gef\u00fchrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb \u00fcbernimmt Deutschland in zunehmendem Ma\u00dfe weltweit Verantwortung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Mali beispielsweise leistet die Bundeswehr einen substanziellen Beitrag zur Stabilisierung dieser wichtigen Transitregion f\u00fcr Fl\u00fcchtlinge in Afrika. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von Jordanien aus beteiligt sie sich am Kampf gegen die menschenverachtenden Schl\u00e4chter des IS. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Afghanistan hilft sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit das Land den m\u00fchsam begonnenen Weg zur Freiheit und zur Selbstst\u00e4ndigkeit weitergehen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.160", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All diese verschiedenen Eins\u00e4tze sind wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.560", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie bedeuten aber auch gestiegene Anforderungen an die Truppe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.080", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So unterschiedlich die Eins\u00e4tze und Bedrohungen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so unterschiedlich m\u00fcssen auch die F\u00e4higkeiten der Bundeswehr sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um darauf reagieren zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher muss die Bundeswehr ihre F\u00e4higkeiten erhalten und ihre Kapazit\u00e4ten erweitern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn sowohl Mensch als auch Material d\u00fcrfen nicht \u00fcberbelastet werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der zus\u00e4tzliche Bedarf der Bundeswehr an Ausr\u00fcstung und an Material ist dabei unbestritten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Zusammenhang sind bewaffnungsf\u00e4hige Drohnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schwere Transporthubschrauber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "neue Cybereinheiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.160", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommunikation und vieles andere wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.400", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All das sind Schl\u00fcsselsysteme f\u00fcr die zuk\u00fcnftige Einsatzbereitschaft der Bundeswehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All das kostet auch Geld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.920", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist gut investiert f\u00fcr unsere Zukunft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.560", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Sicherheit unseres Landes."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben den Auslandseins\u00e4tzen der Bundeswehr erfordert jedoch auch die neue NATO-Abschreckungsstrategie bessere Verteidigungsf\u00e4higkeiten von uns. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.960", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland ist gegen\u00fcber dem B\u00fcndnis Verpflichtungen eingegangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das auch aus gutem Grund. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.640", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir d\u00fcrfen hinter diesen Verpflichtungen nicht zur\u00fcckbleiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist das 2-Prozent-Ziel f\u00fcr uns eine wichtige Marke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.120", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der wir nachkommen m\u00fcssen und wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.760", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als europ\u00e4ische Rahmennation der NATO und als Anlehnungspartner innerhalb der Europ\u00e4ischen Sicherheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Verteidigungspolitik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.801", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir durch die PESCO-Initiative fortentwickeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.280", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stehen wir in der Verantwortung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.480", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere F\u00e4higkeiten auszubauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um sie in die Gemeinschaft in Europa einbringen zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch unsere Beteiligung an der NATO-Pr\u00e4senz im Baltikum und in Polen st\u00e4rken wir das transatlantische B\u00fcndnis in Europa und nehmen Sicherheitsinteressen unserer \u00f6stlichen Partner ernst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.960", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die NATO, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.080", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.160", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist f\u00fcr uns kein Anachronismus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch 28\u00a0Jahre nach dem Ende des Kalten Krieges ist das B\u00fcndnis unverzichtbares R\u00fcckgrat unserer deutschen und europ\u00e4ischen Sicherheitsstruktur."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.080", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade in Zeiten eines russischen Hegemonialstrebens im postsowjetischen Raum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.081", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das im Westen weit nach Europa hineinreicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.120", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Bedeutung der NATO f\u00fcr unser aller Sicherheit so wichtig wie seit dem Fall des Eisernen Vorhangs nicht mehr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.121", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.121", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das russische Gro\u00dfman\u00f6ver an der \u00adNATO-Ostgrenze im letzten Jahr hat Russlands Ambitionen und sein milit\u00e4risches Potenzial eindrucksvoll unter Beweis gestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.200", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Landes- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.080", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und B\u00fcndnisverteidigung haben durch die zunehmende offensive Au\u00dfenpolitik Russlands in unseren Planungen einen neuen Stellenwert bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.120", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist leider die Realit\u00e4t, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und diese Realit\u00e4t kostet Geld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus diesem Grund ist es umso bedauerlicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute einen Antrag beraten m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.840", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nicht nur unsere B\u00fcndnisf\u00e4higkeit gef\u00e4hrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch die NATO in Europa schw\u00e4chen w\u00fcrde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.440", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.720", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bundeswehr wird in den n\u00e4chsten Jahren einen Spagat hinlegen m\u00fcssen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie muss sowohl f\u00fcr die B\u00fcndnisverteidigung gewappnet sein als auch f\u00fcr ihre Auslandseins\u00e4tze auf der ganzen Welt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir Deutschlands Verantwortung nachkommen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Spagat kann die Bundeswehr nur durch eine Erh\u00f6hung der Verteidigungsausgaben meistern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Bundestag sollten im Sinne unserer Soldatinnen und Soldaten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.200", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die tagt\u00e4glich im Dienst f\u00fcr unsere Sicherheit sind und dabei oft ihr Leben riskieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unserer gestiegenen Verantwortung gerecht werden und die Bundeswehr ad\u00e4quat f\u00fcr diese Anforderungen ausstatten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.840", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland muss in Zukunft mehr f\u00fcr seine Sicherheit tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.920", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.200", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Redezeit ist abgelaufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir die Bundeswehr fit f\u00fcr die Zukunft machen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.440", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir mehr Geld als bisher ausgeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.441", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind wir unseren Soldatinnen und Soldaten und unserer Verantwortung schuldig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.441", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.442", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
